net.proteusframework.internet.dataprovider

Class JavaScriptInitProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.internet.dataprovider.JavaScriptInitProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataProvider

    public class JavaScriptInitProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataProvider
    Data Provider whose purpose is to provide initialization data for a script tag.

    This should be registered before the rendering phase in the case of the results of rendering being cached.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@proteus.co)
